N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 606.134 - Judicial review

Parties dissatisfied with the final apportionment
determination may elect to challenge such apportionment pursuant to article 78
of the New York Civil Practice Law and Rules. Notes
